title: Formula.Truck.Simulator.2013-HI2U
description:
HI2U!

Formula Truck Simulator 2013 (v1.10) (c) Reiza Studios

Release date : 24th of August, 2013
Protection   : Gameshield
Type         : Simulation
Size         : 75 x 50 mb

Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Developed by Reiza Studios for Windows PC, Formula Truck Simulator simulates
Formula Trucks 2013 season and includes 26 race trucks and drivers, plus 14
minutely detailed race tracks for a total of 18 different layouts. The player
is able to set up his truck by adjusting suspension, drivetrain, brakes and
tires in order to reach the best performance.

Install:
~~~~~~~
Extract & mount the iso and install.
Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory on the image to your
game install directory. Play the game. Buy it if you like it.
